Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:19.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fumizuki Academy is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:24.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a prep school that implemented{\i0}\N{\i1}the world's first special systems.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:27.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, please start.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:33.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One of them is the Summoner Test War.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:35.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is a battle between classes using{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.62,0:00:38.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Avatars realized using{\i0}\N{\i1}state-of-the-art technology.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:42.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the other is classroom equipment{\i0}\N{\i1}based on the students' performance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:44.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the end of the first year,{\i0}\N{\i1}they take a placement test.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:48.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Based on the results,{\i0}\N{\i1}they are divided into 6 levels,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:51.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}from the top, Class A,{\i0}\N{\i1}through the bottom, Class F.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.39,0:00:57.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is the placement test.{\i0}\N{\i1}It's difficult, as is to be expected...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.27,0:00:59.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I can handle something this difficult.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:10.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.61,0:01:14.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.99,0:01:19.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:22.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Himeji? Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:26.54,Main,,0,0,0,,If you leave the room during the test,\Nyou'll receive zeroes. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.54,0:01:27.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.63,0:01:28.75,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it, Yoshii?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.75,0:01:32.51,Main,,0,0,0,,How can she help it if she's sick?!\NGiving her a zero for that is cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:35.09,Main,,0,0,0,,--Staying healthy is also...\N--Yoshi... i...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:43.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You're late, Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.69,0:01:44.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Iron Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:47.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Not Iron Man! Call me Mr. Nishimura!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:49.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Here. You're the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:52.78,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the result of the placement test.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:01:55.45,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll belong to that class from today on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:57.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:01:58.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.37,0:01:58.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:01.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I can tell you this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:04.71,Main,,0,0,0,,While watching you over the last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.71,0:02:08.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I had a suspicion... that\Nyou might actually be an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:10.00,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:14.93,Main,,0,0,0,,But looking at your test results,\NI realized that was my mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:20.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Yoshii. I shouldn't\Nhave doubted you. I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:25.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You are, beyond any doubt,\Nthe real deal... a genuine idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:39.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What grows on its own? Hmm, what is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:42.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more chance, one more{\i0}\N{\i1}chance. Never never give up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:45.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more chance, one{\i0}\N{\i1}more chance. Never give up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:54.34,Main,,0,0,0,,BAKA and TEST\N-Summon the Beasts-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:58.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Nice to encounter you,"{\i0}\N{\i1}that one's too easy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:03:00.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's only one answer{\i0}\N{\i1}that I decided on at the start{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:03.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My heart fluttered. Will I pass?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:06.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't panic whether{\i0}\N{\i1}it's a matter of love or war{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:08.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sigh as I cram all night long{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:11.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a genius dreamer inside of me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:14.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'd be nice if everything I wanted came true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:16.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pay no mind to other people's worlds{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:19.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect-area complete!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:21.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll definitely be waiting right here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:28.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect-area, I can hear someone wishing for it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:29.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah! Ear! Ear!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:32.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why? We just keep missing each other{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:35.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you came to me for advice, it'd go like{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:38.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"So, friends?" "Yes, friends."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:39.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a sad 0 points.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:43.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! Do it again! Rewrite it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:45.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I'm serious, one{\i0}\N{\i1}more chance please{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:50.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know, there's a future{\i0}\N{\i1}more wonderful than now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:56.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make it more wonderful than{\i0}\N{\i1}now... my life, my life, my life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.03,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Episode 1" "Idiots, Classes, and the Summoner Test War"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.16,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Episode 1" "Idiots, Classes, and the Summoner Test War"\N{\i1}Fumizuki Academy is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:06.08,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Episode 1" "Idiots, Classes, and the Summoner Test War"\N{\i1}a prep school that implemented the world's first special systems.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:06.54,Main,,0,0,0,,"Try very hard."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:08.50,Main,,0,0,0,,"Try very hard."\NWhy Class F?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:10.17,Main,,0,0,0,,"Akihisa Yoshii"\NThat's the lowest ranked class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:12.79,Main,,0,0,0,,"Akihisa Yoshii"\NI was so sure I did okay in the placement test.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I answered at least one\Nout of every ten questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:15.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fumizuki Academy is{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:22.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a prep school that takes pride{\i0}\N{\i1}in having the latest equipment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:27.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Workstations and reclining chairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:30.14,Main,,0,0,0,,They're provided with laptops?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:34.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! They've got free drink\Nfountains and all-you-can-eat snacks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:36.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous of Class A!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:45.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tatami {\i0}mats? Cushions? Low tables?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:48.25,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the Class F classroom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:50.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fumizuki Academy is ruthless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:53.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you wish to have a better{\i0}\N{\i1}school life, do better in school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:56.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is the law of this academy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:59.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Is this what you call a social divide?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:02.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii. Please hurry up and take your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:03.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:05.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Where's my seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:07.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Have a seat wherever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:10.06,Main,,0,0,0,,We don't even get assigned seats?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:15.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Teacher, my cushion\Nhas very little cotton in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:17.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Please bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:18.65,Main,,0,0,0,,"Whoosh"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:21.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Teacher! The draft is cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:23.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Please bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:29.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Teacher! One of the legs\Nof my low table got broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:30.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Please bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I was just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:37.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, Fumizuki Academy is ruthless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:42.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm your homeroom teacher, Fukuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:46.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I look forward to teaching\Nyou this year, everyon--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:50.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go get some tools, so please\Nstudy on your own until I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:52.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously, this classroom is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:56.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to spend a year in\Nthis place? How depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:57.40,Main,,0,0,0,,If you have complaints,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.19,Main,,0,0,0,,you should've gotten better\Nscores on the placement test.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:01.57,Main,,0,0,0,,"Yuuji Sakamoto"\NYuuji! You're in Class F, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:03.70,Main,,0,0,0,,"Yuuji Sakamoto"\NNot just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:06.37,Main,,0,0,0,,"Minami Shimada"\NHello, hello. I'm in Class F, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:11.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Shimada... I see... It makes sense\Nthat you'd be in Class F, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:13.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to say I'm an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:15.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Ouch, ouch, ouch! Since you don't have breasts,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:19.42,Main,,0,0,0,,my ears are rubbing against your ribs!\NIt hurts so much worse than norma--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:27.89,Main,,0,0,0,,"Kouta Tsuchiya"\NI-I can almost see it, but not... not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:31.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I grew up abroad, so I can't read\Nthe questions in Japanese. That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:34.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You guys are lively, as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:35.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Hideyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:38.77,Main,,0,0,0,,"Hideyoshi Kinoshita"\NI'm in Class F, too. Glad to see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:41.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Same here. Glad to see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:44.74,Main,,0,0,0,,At any rate, just as you'd expect\Nfrom the lowest performing class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:48.28,Main,,0,0,0,,As far as the eye can see,\NI see only shabby guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:49.95,Main,,0,0,0,,That includes you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:53.87,Main,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad... that the only girl\Nhere is a pretty girl like you, Hideyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:56.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:58.33,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Girls are kind and graceful,\Nand have this soothing aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:03.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Just looking at them puts our hearts at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:06.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone like you who's rough,\Nviolent and scary with no breas--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:09.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel a severe pain in my spine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:14.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm... I'm sorry that I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:17.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I went to the nurse's office\Nand it took a while, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:19.86,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Mizuki Himeji"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:22.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:24.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:24.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh... how cute she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:28.74,Main,,0,0,0,,--Why is someone like her in Class F?\N--I'm so glad I'm in Class F!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:30.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:32.79,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it... Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:36.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:40.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh! My spine has never been\Nbent this way in my entire life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:44.46,Main,,0,0,0,,--Ahhh! If it gets bent further, I'm gonna...\N--Almost... Almost...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:52.14,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Twitch, twitch, twitch..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:53.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Muttsulini!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:54.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:55.73,Main,,0,0,0,,L... L...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:58.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't talk! We'll call a doctor right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:07:59.94,Main,,0,0,0,,L... Light blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:02.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Muttsulini!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.57,Main,,0,0,0,,--I'm glad that there's another girl in the class.\N--Muttsulini! Are you okay?! Your wound isn't deep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:05.65,Main,,0,0,0,,--Seats are not assigned\N--Muttsulini! Are you okay?! Your wound isn't deep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.99,Main,,0,0,0,,--so we were told to sit wherever we like.\N--Muttsulini! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:07.78,Main,,0,0,0,,--so we were told to sit wherever we like.\N--Help! Somebody, please help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:10.12,Main,,0,0,0,,--Okay. Thank you very much.\N--Help! Somebody, please help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:10.41,Main,,0,0,0,,--Then...\N--Help! Somebody, please help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:11.45,Main,,0,0,0,,--Then...\N--Doctor! Is there a doctor in the house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:13.03,Main,,0,0,0,,--Is that seat open?\N--Doctor! Is there a doctor in the house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:15.83,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:20.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. You're in Class F, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:23.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to\Nstudying with you, Yoshii...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:25.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you still sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:27.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:31.43,Main,,0,0,0,,The drafty classroom... Thin cushions...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:33.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Old {\i1}tatami {\i0}mats with\Nmold and dust floating about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:36.93,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not a good environment for\Nsomeone who's still recuperating, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:52.12,Main,,0,0,0,,So, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:56.08,Main,,0,0,0,,This is what I think. Schools\Nare a microcosm of society, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:59.04,Main,,0,0,0,,There shouldn't be discriminatory\Ninequality among classes like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:00.96,Main,,0,0,0,,But no matter what we,\Nthe lowest ranked students, say,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:02.96,Main,,0,0,0,,it's considered only the grumblings of a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:04.67,Main,,0,0,0,,So we should challenge other\Nclasses to a fight fair and square,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:06.80,Main,,0,0,0,,and obtain the power and right to\Nspeak first. Then we should cast this issue...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:10.47,Main,,0,0,0,,In other words, you wanna improve\Nour classroom equipment for Himeji, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:12.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm beating around the\Nbush because it's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:13.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to rephrase it bluntly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:17.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. To tell you the truth,\NI was thinking about starting a war, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:19.10,Main,,0,0,0,,What? You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:24.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I wanted to prove that\Nacademic ability isn't all that matters in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:28.11,Main,,0,0,0,,And... we do stand a chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:29.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna try, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:33.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's do it! Let's call\Nfor a Summoner Test War!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:38.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone, listen! As the Class F Rep,\NI'd like to make a proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:42.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of having us,\NClass F, start a Summoner Test War.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:44.13,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,A Summoner Test War...? Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:48.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At Fumizuki Academy,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:52.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there's a system called Summoner{\i0}\N{\i1}Test War, also known as ST War.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:54.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With a teacher present,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:56.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a student can summon their{\i0}\N{\i1}Avatar, whose offense power{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:59.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is based on the student's{\i0}\N{\i1}performance in that subject.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:01.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Students fight using their Avatars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:03.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By defeating a higher-ranked{\i0}\N{\i1}class, they can exchange{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:07.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}their classroom equipment with{\i0}\N{\i1}the higher ranked class's equipment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:10.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone, aren't you unhappy\Nwith this shabby classroom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Heck yeah we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:14.15,Main,,0,0,0,,But if we can just win in a ST War,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:19.45,Main,,0,0,0,,we can even get our hands on\Nthat gorgeous Class A equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:22.58,Main,,0,0,0,,We're the lowest ranked students!\NWe're at the very bottom of the academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:27.04,Main,,0,0,0,,We're a group of scum noticed\Nby no one and below everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:31.05,Main,,0,0,0,,In other words, that\Nmeans we have nothing to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:33.51,Main,,0,0,0,,So why don't we try?! There's no harm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:36.14,Main,,0,0,0,,In addition, we have this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:37.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:45.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Believe it or not, this guy, Akihisa\NYoshii, is a probationary student!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:46.27,Main,,0,0,0,,He's a probationary student?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:48.73,Main,,0,0,0,,--I didn't know we had a guy like that in this class.\N--Incredible... This is my first time seeing one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:50.23,Main,,0,0,0,,--Purify the room with salt!\N--I'm in despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:53.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not all that special...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:55.11,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it, Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:57.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Is a probationary\Nstudent really that incredible?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:11:00.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's not like anyone can become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:01.54,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a special treatment
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:03.79,Main,,0,0,0,,for a trouble student\Nwhose school performance is bad
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:04.75,Main,,0,0,0,,and who lacks a desire to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:06.79,Main,,0,0,0,,It's also said to be a synonym for "idiot."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:09.29,Main,,0,0,0,,It's someone who's completely useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that's really incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:13.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! I wanna crawl under the rug if we had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:17.97,Main,,0,0,0,,If we win in a ST War, we can say\Ngoodbye to this shabby classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:20.30,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you say, everyone?! Do you wanna try?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:22.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:25.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, to start with, we'll\Ndefeat the next rank up, Class E!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:29.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa! As an ambassador for\NClass F, go declare war against Class E.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:31.19,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:34.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Normally, a lower-ranked class'\Nmessenger who declares war
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:35.65,Main,,0,0,0,,is given hell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:38.32,Main,,0,0,0,,That's something that\Nhappens in movies and novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:41.28,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way they'd do rude things\Nto an important ambassador, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:43.29,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:47.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa. This is an important\Nmission that only you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:49.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Please just trust me and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:53.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:55.09,Main,,0,0,0,,You lied!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:56.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I figured as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:57.51,Main,,0,0,0,,So you expected this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:12:00.01,Main,,0,0,0,,One is unfit to be a class rep\Nif he can't expect that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:01.68,Main,,0,0,0,,At least try to sound sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:05.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, we can't go back, Akihisa. Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.93,0:12:09.60,Main,,0,0,0,,--What?\N--This is what you want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:13.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Bring it on any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:15.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? This year's Year 2 students
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:18.86,Main,,0,0,0,,are trying to call for a ST War\Non the first day of the first term?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:21.57,Main,,0,0,0,,How interesting. Approve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:23.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:26.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, how will it turn out? We'll see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:29.08,Main,,0,0,0,,"Approved"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.58,Main,,0,0,0,,"Hasegawa"\N"Culture Club Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:33.71,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll use Mr. Hasegawa as\Nthe attending teacher for the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:37.17,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll secure him on his\Nway to Class E for fifth period.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:40.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hasegawa... Then the subject will be math?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:42.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm good at math.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:46.18,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll use math, the subject\NShimada's good at, as our main strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:47.85,Main,,0,0,0,,How are you with math, Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:50.10,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm bad at it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:52.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, you can fight with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:53.98,Main,,0,0,0,,No, she can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:55.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:59.61,Main,,0,0,0,,The scores on the last test we took\Nbecome our Avatars' offense power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:01.99,Main,,0,0,0,,The test we took last is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:04.28,Main,,0,0,0,,The placement test...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:07.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Since I left the room in the middle\Nof the test, my scores are all zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:08.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:13.50,Main,,0,0,0,,But once the ST War starts,\Nshe can take a recovery test.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:16.67,Main,,0,0,0,,If she takes that test, she can\Nparticipate midway into the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:18.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:20.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:22.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:39.69,Main,,0,0,0,,We've secured Mr. Hasegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:42.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Start the war! Everyone, start the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:48.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Geez... For idiots, they're pretty cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:52.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone, time to attack!\NTeach Class F a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:53.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:02.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Minami Shimada! I'm fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:05.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Hideyoshi Kinoshita!\NI'm participating in the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:07.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Kouta Tsuchiya! Ditto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:09.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:14.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm summoning my Avatar. Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:17.32,Main,,0,0,0,,"Name: Minami Shimada"\N"Subject: Math" "Score: 89"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:22.78,Main,,0,0,0,,"Name: Kouta Tsuchiya"\N"Subject: Math" "Score: 25"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:24.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:43.84,Main,,0,0,0,,"Name: Hideyoshi Kinoshita"\N"Subject: Math" "Score: 76"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:46.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Why am I the only one who transformed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:48.10,Main,,0,0,0,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:55.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Please be careful. Real humans\Ncan't pass through that area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:58.61,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to pass through\Nhere, you have to defeat us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:01.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshiko Mikami, I accept this challenge! Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:03.90,Main,,0,0,0,,"Name: Yoshiko Mikami"\N"Subject: Math" "Score: 81"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:07.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:08.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Here's the finishing blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:10.45,Main,,0,0,0,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:15.16,Main,,0,0,0,,When it comes to math,\NI won't lose against Class E!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:17.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Those who died, meet me\Nin the remedial classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:18.29,Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Iron Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:21.05,Main,,0,0,0,,In accordance with the Summoner Test War Rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:23.92,Main,,0,0,0,,those who died with their score reduced\Nto zero will be given a remedial class!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:29.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Help! I don't wanna take a\Nremedial class taught by a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:32.47,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to pass through\Nhere, you have to defeat us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:35.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. Then that's what we'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:38.48,Main,,0,0,0,,--Summon!\N--Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:40.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:41.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:43.94,Main,,0,0,0,,"Replenish Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:45.95,Main,,0,0,0,,"Recovery Test"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:49.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, if you're ready, please start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.87,0:15:53.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What's your strategy, Yuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:54.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:55.16,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:57.12,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a power game that depends on force,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:16:00.04,Main,,0,0,0,,so the enemy rushes into the\Nclassroom of the overwhelmed side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:02.59,Main,,0,0,0,,And the class whose rep gets defeated loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:05.01,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way we'd be overwhelmed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:07.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Trouble! We're gonna be overwhelmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:08.26,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:10.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Class E's school\Nperformance is better than ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:13.76,Main,,0,0,0,,So if we fight in a straightforward way,\Nit's only a matter of time before we lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:15.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:20.06,Main,,0,0,0,,But they're only Class E after all.\NThey're not much different from Class F.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:24.82,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll take time to overwhelm us.\NThat time is the key to our victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:28.78,Main,,0,0,0,,My score is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:31.41,Main,,0,0,0,,As it stands, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:33.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Step back and go recover your score!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:35.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:43.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll take the recovery test!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:45.46,Main,,0,0,0,,The score of this test will be your score
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:48.42,Main,,0,0,0,,when you summon your Avatar next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:52.35,Main,,0,0,0,,If you get a lower score, your\NAvatar will get weaker instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:53.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:56.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Which subject would you like to take?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:58.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Math, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:02.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to answer as many{\i0}\N{\i1}as I can to get a better score!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:04.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't fight any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:06.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Muttsulini!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:09.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's take a strategic withdrawal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:12.62,Main,,0,0,0,,This battle is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:22.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:24.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Attack them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:25.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Sounds like our line of defense has been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:29.63,Main,,0,0,0,,--Summon!\N--This is bad, Yuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.47,0:17:33.89,Main,,0,0,0,,"Recovery Test"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:35.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it's just numerical formulas,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:39.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's a breeze as I don't have{\i0}\N{\i1}to be able to read Japanese!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:44.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah! Kanji! I'll skip this and{\i0}\N{\i1}move on to the next question.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:45.65,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Scratch, scratch, scratch..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:54.91,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Bam!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:58.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Those who died, meet me\Nin the remedial classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:01.25,Main,,0,0,0,,What should we do, Yuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:03.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you guys done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:06.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like this is it for\Nyou, huh? Mr. Class F Rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:11.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? The Class E Rep herself\Nmarches in here? How confident you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:13.76,Main,,0,0,0,,The first term just started\Nand you declared a war already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:15.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.76,Main,,0,0,0,,It's right after the placement test,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.85,Main,,0,0,0,,so the difference between us is the\Ndifference between our test scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:21.35,Main,,0,0,0,,You think you have a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:23.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:23.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:27.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You're an idiot who can't figure even\Nthat out. That's why you're in Class F.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:30.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji, without even a strategy,\Nthere's no way we can defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:31.15,Main,,0,0,0,,a higher ranked class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:34.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Come to think of it,\NI did have one strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:35.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:38.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you get why I have you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:40.58,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:45.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:48.80,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. This student, Akihisa\NYoshii, is a probationary student!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:52.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa! Show them your real power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:54.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Tsk. I guess it can't be helped, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:58.47,Main,,0,0,0,,After all, in the end, I'll have\Nto show off my grand skills, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:19:00.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Summon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:05.64,Main,,0,0,0,,The probationary student's\NAvatar has a special ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:08.90,Main,,0,0,0,,As punishment, he has to\Nhelp with the teachers' chores,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:11.61,Main,,0,0,0,,so his Avatar can actually touch objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:14.24,Main,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:19.28,Main,,0,0,0,,--Ow, ow, ow, ow... My head...!\N--the Summoner receives the same pain that his Avatar receives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:20.79,Main,,0,0,0,,See, isn't it interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:22.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:25.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll take care of that small fry first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:26.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:30.13,Main,,0,0,0,,We won't lose so easily. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:40.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh! He hit the same spot! It hurts! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:43.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Just as you'd expect from the\NClass E Rep. You're not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:45.56,Main,,0,0,0,,He's such a useless guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:48.73,Main,,0,0,0,,No... He was very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:55.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, as the Rep,\NI'll put an end to this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:20:02.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Be prepared. Class E Rep, Hiromi\NNakabayashi! I challenge Yuuji Saka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:04.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:07.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Mizuki Himeji! I accept this challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:10.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm summoning my Avatar! Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:11.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:18.30,Main,,0,0,0,,What's with that score?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:19.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Her offense power is as high as Class A!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:22.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is such a student in Class F?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:23.60,Main,,0,0,0,,She's finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:24.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:27.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Mizuki Himeji...? Don't tell me you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:28.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:29.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Shimada?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:32.02,Main,,0,0,0,,She's really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:43.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Just as you'd expect from her.\NShe wasn't a Class A candidate for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:45.99,Main,,0,0,0,,That's Himeji's score?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:47.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Fumizuki Academy's tests have\Nan unlimited number of questions
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.71,Main,,0,0,0,,in a limited time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:51.79,Main,,0,0,0,,So long as you can answer,\Nyour score doesn't have a limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:53.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Then the strategy you mentioned was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:56.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Buying some time for her to take the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:59.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't told such a person is in Class F!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:02.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, here I come! I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:03.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:07.14,Main,,0,0,0,,"Class F Win"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:13.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And thus, this Summoner Test War{\i0}\N{\i1}ended with a victory by Class F.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:18.57,Main,,0,0,0,,All right! You're amazing, Himeji!\NThis is all thanks to your power, Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:21.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:25.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Now we can exchange our classroom\Nequipment with Class E's, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:27.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Though it's just a little,\Nthe environment will be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:30.62,Main,,0,0,0,,No, we won't exchange our equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:31.54,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:33.71,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll keep the same equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:36.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a nice proposal, Miss Class E Rep?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:38.67,Main,,0,0,0,,What...? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:42.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Why, Yuuji?! We fought hard and won the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it settled?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:48.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you dressed like that, Hideyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:51.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see! You've finally\Nawakened to your true self, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:53.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa, I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:55.65,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Two Hideyoshis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:21:57.28,Main,,0,0,0,,That's my older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:22:00.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Hideyoshi is my little twin brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:04.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Yuuko Kinoshita,\Nan ambassador from Year 2, Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,We, Class A, hereby declare war on you, Class F!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:11.00,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:12.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is Class A declaring war on us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:15.63,Main,,0,0,0,,We won't go easy on you just\Nbecause you're the lowest ranked class.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:18.80,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll crush you mercilessly, so be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:28.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}B-A-K-A Go Go Home!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.60,0:22:34.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}B-A-K-A Go Go Home!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.77,0:22:37.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The end of the school day is bliss{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:40.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I am to put it into words, "It's really angelic!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:43.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My peace was shattered{\i0}\N{\i1}by a sudden announcement{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.82,0:22:46.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Talking about the make up test. "This is Hell!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:49.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While my friends and I were{\i0}\N{\i1}sharing funny stories, I said,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.95,0:22:52.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"There's no way anyone is that stupid"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.96,0:22:56.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the truth is, deep down in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:23:00.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was shouting, "That was me!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:06.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}About that "Monthly Parking"{\i0}\N{\i1}sign you see in the parking lot{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:12.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought it was the name of a company...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.10,0:23:15.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All this time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.56,0:23:18.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sticking to your idiocy can be cool{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:21.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is our common sense nonsense?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.65,0:23:24.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We don't need rules in this world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.70,0:23:27.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's dog eat dog food! It's social upheaval!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.70,0:23:29.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:33.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sun that rose from the west is setting{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:36.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Run home! It's dinner time already.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:44.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go home! Let's go home!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.93,0:23:52.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Question 2.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.97,0:23:55.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Name the plant that has a subterranean{\i0}\N{\i1}stem that sometimes is edible{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.10,0:23:57.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and is called "lily" in English.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:23:59.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yam potato! Potato! Sweet potato!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.31,0:24:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please don't just focus on the word "edible."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.82,0:24:03.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode! "Lilies, Roses,{\i0}\N{\i1}and Health and Physical Education!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.94,0:24:05.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This will be on the test.{\i0}
